      </para>

      <para>
      The Qgar software is entirely developed in C++, for Unix/Linux OS. The source code includes about 50,000 lines and may 
      be freely downloaded, together with its installation/compilation tools as well as the HTML version of the documentation, 
      from the Qgar software web site See button '<emphasis>Downloads</emphasis>' in the menu on the left. A click on the Qgar logo makes you go 
      to the Qgar software web site.
      </para>

